{"tid":940302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不同政黨2男議員　在議會廁所啪啪啪被抓包","createTime":"2018-12-14T00:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T01:40:53.000Z","uid":141151,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"87a707f6302e35ec6cb03b4c700f7530eac19105","tid":940302,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T00:02:24.000Z","msg":"不同政黨2男議員　在議會廁所啪啪啪被抓包<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181212/1482636/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181212%2F1482636%2F&d=Xm7WKmrItRA9qTfGUjZ%2Fa0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9ef7f1ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181212%2F1482636%2F&h=e53660eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181212/1482636/</a><br />\n<br />\n義大利兩名不同政黨的男議員，在議會廁所發生性關係，被其他使用廁所的人用手機拍下後曝光。<br />\n<br />\n據《衛星通訊社》報導，義大利日報（il Giornale）記者劉易佐(Romana Liuzzo)指出，兩名國會議員，一名隸屬五星運動黨(Movimento Cinque Stelle），另一名議員則是北方聯盟黨(Lega Nord），他們在議會的廁所發生性關係，「我們都知道他們的名字」但是記者拒絕透露他們的身分，理由是他們擁有隱私權。<br />\n<br />\n不過有媒體給出線索，稱這2人都是高大帥氣的男人。據悉，五星運動黨的領導人下令禁止任何黨員討論此事。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9259af8487d2430423dbc7d31eebe68e86fb5ce5","tid":940302,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T00:07:21.000Z","msg":"係愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e18ae39576d2a943ce01d9183ce83136aa24b2","tid":940302,"uid":33477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T00:09:55.000Z","msg":"估錯地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142bdac9ec71e7eb47406916b2472b47789fce56","tid":940302,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12